oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Carburetor on an Internal Combustion Engine
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Students; Engineering; Scientific equipment; Engines
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Bruce Inman (Class of 1966, Electrical Engineering) demonstrates a computer controlled carburetor, a project he completed in collaboration with fellow student, Edward M. Grashot, for their senior project. A copy of their report, E III C Mod I (Electronic Computer Controlled Carburetion, is available in Plough Library.
